---
---

<section id="founder" class="founder-section">
  <div class="container founder-inner">
    <p class="eyebrow founder-eyebrow reveal">From the founder</p>
    <h2 class="founder-pull-quote reveal">
      "I spent ten years helping people build health products. The frustrating
      part was never the data. It was that no single product could see across it."
    </h2>
    <div class="founder-body reveal">
      <p>
        Your ring sees your sleep. Your watch sees your workouts. Your scale sees
        your weight. None of them talk. So you end up being the synthesizer,
        squinting at four apps before breakfast.
      </p>
      <p>
        Meld is the product I wanted. It reads all of it, finds what actually
        moves your numbers, and tells you the one thing to try today. No
        dashboards. No coaching speak. Just signal.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="founder-sig reveal">
      <div class="founder-avatar" aria-hidden="true">BH</div>
      <div>
        <div class="founder-name">Brock Howard</div>
        <div class="founder-title">Founder · 15+ years in consumer health</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .founder-section {
    padding-block: var(--section-pad-y);
    background: var(--purple-50);
  }

  .founder-inner {
    max-width: 820px;
  }

  .founder-eyebrow {
    color: var(--purple-600);
  }

  .founder-pull-quote {
    font-family: var(--font-family);
    font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 3.5vw, 2.5rem);
    font-weight: var(--fw-thin);
    font-style: italic;
    line-height: 1.2;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    margin-top: var(--sp-4);
    margin-bottom: var(--sp-8);
    text-wrap: balance;
  }

  .founder-body p {
    font-size: var(--fs-body);
    font-weight: var(--fw-light);
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    margin-bottom: var(--sp-4);
    max-width: none;
  }

  .founder-sig {
    margin-top: var(--sp-8);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 14px;
  }

  .founder-avatar {
    width: 44px;
    height: 44px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--purple-200);
    display: grid;
    place-items: center;
    font-weight: var(--fw-medium);
    color: var(--purple-600);
    font-size: 15px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .founder-name {
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: var(--fw-medium);
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }

  .founder-title {
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: var(--fw-light);
    color: var(--text-tertiary);
  }
</style>
